b/101796983449688064541"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Downtown","street":"15809 Bear Creek Pkwy #305","city":"Redmond","postal_code":"98052","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Repair services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Kyler Johan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK-Gj8bPFB4oXcuFO9Y48NhCrgcH7G-lMI6_wVlVHMPWOhYmA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The plumber showed up on time and got straight to work. He cleared our main drain blockage without any mess. I appreciated how organized and prepared he was. Pricing was explained upfront with no surprises. Good service overall.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jessica Qiu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWI9eeckFSJAikWBSFaTW9hwHGxGWXrU3QE7Zh2xrY2yY8Hz2Fy0A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I called asking to get an estimate. I apparently made the mistake of telling the man on the phone that I had already gotten one estimate from a different plumber. The man instantly changed his tone and became rude, acting like it's not okay for me to get multiple estimates. Even though their website clearly states that they offer free estimates, he told me that because I previously had a different plumber out, they would not do a free estimate for me. Their website is a joke, claiming that they offer friendly service.\n\nAfter hanging up, I received an extremely inappropriate and unprofessional text message, which I've attached here.\n\nIt is completely normal for people to get multiple quotes for things like plumbing. That's literally what homeowners do when looking for someone to complete work. It is not the customer's problem that the company gets billed for phone calls. That's just part of doing business.\n\nThe behavior I experienced today from this company is a huge red flag and I would never recommend them.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3gd-n3IXXZaUdK8mkZjV0uB_S9-ZAqCxEh84gvfWqKlqHLqEcodFCScgYEtUKPJCs-o0sZ2MkdSUc-iDpyeSHLxecH9vYOyYALn6Ee5pp84-6LgLacZz99pE-GiVmDeWdnaPdENDbcfr2S=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-10"},{"Name":"Oscar Malone","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU6lFvnzjEiZ_4u45bHQ3dtUGR2TOtL62TazTn3U-Q3J-h8UKU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Communication before the visit was clear and not overly formal. Just simple messages that made sense. He showed up close to the expected time. Fixed the issue without making it feel dramatic. Sometimes plumbing problems feel overwhelming, but this didn’t.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Liam Isabelle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIRCAgEWMxTMLR-lrFn8PtCANiBfyfTEuNa1q2jN1NkakofHQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A worn out sump pump that struggled during storms was upgraded to a more powerful and efficient model. Testing confirmed it activates quickly and discharges water properly. Recent heavy rainfall proved the system works exactly as it should.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Leila Agustin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI_OzulVHcT_Hh6Q9vsdk15zTejxFkVeKTlffV5zdyAgIvIQg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The installation of a whole house water softener system improved water feel and reduced mineral buildup. The configuration was adjusted carefully to maintain strong pressure throughout the property.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kenny Josie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJo_j6s3HIphrMtkH1HXG6yMEDb3xB4B83FsvssAYkRnDOaTQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Leaky toilet problem resolved fast. The plumber replaced worn parts. Ensured proper functioning. Great attention to detail.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Noah Harris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbAkLcJwxEfR