tions":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Repair services","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Andrew Nedimyer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU2GeUU5AeZiNTIHl_3NZ-Kk5sxuFfD1gGYHr4D9FRP93ZVxnLE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jay, Anthony and Otto were great. I thought the job would take all day and they were done by 3pm. Highly recommend!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2497_QIeRgGS5CtXYpOt5RWURydnLuER6lKHghEt-ZRHT5FTwSsUcz7gelIRBxmWUn5zDkrnvvcJrTd7K-LjRfHUg28cfnzg7HXLn5fChBgN-m6NS3vMQlQbcx73xcAvhqtH8mVYW5bPk=k-no"],"When":"2025-12-12"},{"Name":"Lisa S.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVw-5cJjbBHKpNNh-pT0zUXQkKt-nzuHSoyvpXAMT5gNqn6Ypau=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Many years of reliable service! Austin, Tony, Brady, Cole and Otto came through Xmas week when my old gas furnace finally had to be replaced. I’m now enjoying my new heat pump, and am grateful for the no interest payment plan they provided access to. Thanks guys!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lance Alder","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUQDpzcFQFuNGOv3zrUs16NQueQrCNrOEdGPf660v3PTDY2vXej2w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My 6-year-old mini-split system stopped working due to a refrigerant leak. I had a different company come out and their first recommendation was to replace THE WHOLE SYSTEM at $20,000++!! That is insane for a whole-house system less than a decade old.\nA friend recommended Ballard Natural Gas, and I’m so glad they did!\nThey came out and diagnosed the leak, but couldn’t immediately find it. They only charged for a refrigerant refill \u0026 diagnostics, and the account rep figured out a good plan to move forward. Since the problem was not directly resolved, they came out several more times free of charge to re-attempt to find the leak. Finally, it was determined the leak was in a head unit, which was not the brand BNG usually works with. However, they found a like-for-like replacement, got it ordered and installed, and that seems to have fixed the issue. All told, I ended up paying around $4K. A far cry from the original ‘replace everything’ mentality of the competitors. On top of that, all their technicians and account reps are great to work with! Always friendly and professional, and most importantly, taking a practical and financially sensible approach to address my issue.\nBNG earned my trust and loyalty! I highly recommend them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Martha Clay","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXgHmn01ZgGSFP0NAPPi_7BERHik_wldKN2S8AwZTMReehe_Uc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wonderful service for my heat pump installation.  Respectful to me as a single older woman.   Clear about all the necessary details.  Prompt, on time.  Very tidy.  Treated me like family.  Kudos to Tony, Clint, Zoe!!!, Brady, Cole and DJ","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jeri Howe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJgcKJefAMRSHSARJ73UQ38V1Zq-IJ9oxr61jWM2mEtmYSp9w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We were pleased with all personnel who helped us get our furnace replaced. Everyone knew what they were doing, they were friendly and happy to answer any questions we had. They were efficient and timely. We felt like we were in good hands. Our new furnace is terrific.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rolf Johnson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIlpamQpYH80Ol8UUXywe1Tnv1vz2hs97EeH5eudbHowsUGUA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Clinton and Austin were extremely professional and transparent, and through their explanations and their answers to my questions, they demonstrated their deep knowledge and expertise. It left me with complete confidence in their analysis and suggestions and prepared to choose between the options they presented.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kelland Lindsey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXS0aHMfrFdo6M-SmgyF7aVa_9SWbvfTR7Hs_trSk06H9UU1xko=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Humberto V and Raul G were fantastic and went above and beyond on both a new furnace installation and vent cleaning.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sofia Brindle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJVk6yAmuD4IntIyCu56tcBUYSONAOAmAwxXfqqwQH9meRNfw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Alex Mandziuk was great. He replaced our water heater and furnace in less than six hours, did an excellent job and left everything clean. We highly recommend the service.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
