930","name":"Schmitty's Plumbing (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105250858231939486930"},"complete_address":{"borough":"","street":"","city":"","postal_code":"","state":"","country":""},"about":[{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Online estimates","enabled":false}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Repair services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"crowd","name":"Crowd","options":[{"name":"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Rich Rye","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV3vUtIKxV7AWQJZHYrgtwTe27yEeasHORgXumZE5_ovNyfQzS8tA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My wife and I want to thank the great people at Schmitty's Plumbing for taking great care of a family member recently.\nMy wife's elderly aunt had trouble with a water heater at her redmond home recently. When she called arround to get help she got a lot of jargon hassle very high bids and that left her confused. Luckily she called Schmitty's Plumbing and from the 1st call she felt like she was being taken care of. They kept it simple, arrived same day and patiently explained the options to her. She was able to pick an option that she could afford and they were able to make the replacement the same day.\nVery much appreciated by the family!! Thank you Schmitty's Plumbing!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mark Hammette","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKehTm3z5sP3sKpiVHmCQt7s8Xq_Oz9Y6JXP9frMl1QELhB3Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wow, a breathe of fresh air, this company is awesome!  I asked for and received multiple bids from plumbers.  Schmitty's came out and just fixed my issues in 30 minutes on site, no bid was necessary, get it done mentality, they were prepared and just handled it.  They were friendly, professional, knowledgeable, efficient, prepared, etc, they were fantastic!  I got bids from 5 other companies telling me it would take several hours to fix, for extremely high costs, and it made me really appreciate this company even more.  I highly recommend anyone looking for plumbing needs, they are absolutely excellent!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Peter Lacy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUcQOD2viVJHFVdOoyxTUkI3DWPGrwZMXylNRPv1wmvvGivOEN_=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Highway robbers. I asked about their rates on the phone and she said \"$199 for the visit and then we'll see what's needed.\" The job ended up needing 2 leaky spots tightened: the trap under a sink and the drain spout under the toilet tank. That and a faucet replaced. He was here for less than one hour. The guy charged me $500. My advice: Do NOT hire Schmitty's Plumbing.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Josh E","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLu7oXCp1DdOEBR7mccgVNwMPqN_hdpKaEX8kb7YEOvB10nbQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had my water main start leaking on a sunday night. Brian showed up, got it to stop leaking quickly then went on his way. Great plumber and service.\n\nI also hired Schmitty's Plumbing to install my a new hot water heater and pressure valve regulator. Once again I was very satisfied with my work and service.\n\nI will hire them in the future for my plumbing needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Maggie Sax","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIj_9YeAu9mP099cJHDTiWOdZyl-5a88TqMhPoaKY05YNlu3g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our water heater went out, and I was able to schedule with Schmitty's to have it replaced the next afternoon. the replacement went really well, there were two guys who knew what they were doing, and they even gave us a commercial grade water heater replacement. The price was reasonable and I highly recommend them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"gymnickerson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLI8rkld3CJgIcFJ9rX_ZshKLXUF9NfALD79ZSz4cXs5y2UUZI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A friend recommended this company to me and I am very glad she did.  When I have a plumbing issue it scares me greatly.  I have called the larger companies in the past and have not been satisfied with the impersonal approach and high prices just to get them to my front door.  Schmitty’s Plumbing was prompt (actually early), called a half hour before arriving, and best of all fixed my problem.  The person who was onsite was professional, polite and explained the entire process including a price break down for each level of repair.  I am very happy  I now have a place to call for all my plumbing needs.  I highly recommend them to be your plumber too.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brian Rolf","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUnRcb-vBO1LaezgMwoS_A9Y40NgzsQuutqK6YjetxcrW41zAMf=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had Schmitty's out to fix our \"list\" of plumbing issues. They tackled the easy ones first and then quoted me on the more difficult ones. Brian let me know exactly what they needed to do and the exact cost. We will hire them again once we get another \"list\" together. Thanks for all the hard work with that stuck faucet.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"David Lam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUgn452pJHuxQIBf-sK5f-PA82u-baWKfZsgyIv9oUYUES6ooOXjg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Brian came by during an emergency leak from our main water line to our irrigation.  Prompt, efficient and friendly.  Got the job taken care of quickly and was considerate of our need to have running water.  Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
