ve the opportunity to get multiple bids, and the initial price felt high to us.\n\nI spoke directly with the owner, Steve, afterward. He took the time to walk me through the factors that go into pricing this type of work and how their rates compare to other companies in the area. I appreciated that he was willing to listen to my concerns and make sure I understood the value behind the job. He genuinely wanted us to feel satisfied with both the work and the price.\n\nThe repair was completed quickly and professionally, and based on my conversation with Steve and our overall experience, we plan to hire them again in the near future for other plumbing work. Joseph, the plumber on our job, was definitely our hero when the water started flowing again!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mag 43","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJptP5W9Elp5BMavFcpBZOPxLZXcwN27jUHbB4u-bJl2pp7yQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"There were some communication issues throughout this project. In the end they lived up to their name – Done Right Plumbing! I had a water supply leak in my 25-year-old line, which ran under a paved driveway. Instead of a temporary fix, I wanted a long-term solution. After getting bids from three plumbing companies, Steve from Done Right Plumbing stood out. He assessed my situation (repeatedly) over the phone (in person would have omitted the communication issues), provided a competitive detail quote, and was able to complete the work in a timely fashion. Steve’s crew arrived promptly and got to work right away. Jeremy and co. were professional, tidy, and respectful of my property, I hugely appreciate the efficient service and care shown by Done Right Plumbing! Highly Recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"christina Hendelman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXnCUSWh22g2Ps28aPe9fMIpMAh5akXKqqFnLygnLlVsa0gkvsT=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We chose Done Right because the company was  recommended by neighbors as  we dealt with a very serious failure of our sewer and water pipe system. Our house is quite unusual in its build. Malikai assessed the house with great details to understand better the issues. With great clarity and intelligence he was able to offer a couple of concrete solutions, always aware of the cost associated with each options. We felt very confident that he had our best interest at hand. Malikai is thorough, logical and skilled. He is very much solution oriented. We are very thankful that Malikai was our point person. Wendy in the office was also a pleasure to work with.\nWe will recommend Done Right in the future.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dan McKinnon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIt85Vkow4LLMXZI7Ds2fA0N8eSHDMclJsQUl9g7c6KX5Hzuw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Steve and his team did a great job. They installed a new water service to my house. That was a very difficult project. They use their specialized auger to precisely drill. A new water line that was over 100 feet in length and under a creek and also under my deck in the front yard that was about 20 feet wide at the area where they had to go under without disturbing any of the supports. They were able to complete the job in one day and they have another happy customer.\n\nThanks!!\nDan Mckinnon","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stan Matsui","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVEewZqHfj287o43LZCaegQSJ1wob13SgYU4PzfZFznp-eUuCYCRw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a kitchen sink drainage clog that I couldn't resolve with Drano or a consumer-grade snake. We received a recommendation for Done Right Plumbing, and had them send a plumber to resolve the issue. It turns out there were drywall fragments in the line, apparently from a remodel we had done five years ago. The plumber (Joe) was able to resolve the problem, carefully employing methods to get the work done at a reasonable cost. Would highly recommend them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amy McVay","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVfChWB406ayLG3JocnBaxztp6uDokb58btJJ3vBb5YLOZC6d0B=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very prompt and efficient! On initial callout I was told what the issue was and what I could do to maybe resolve. I was given a quote for repair if I chose. Ultimately I was unable to resolve myself and called for the repair. Jeremy came the following morning and had the repair completed and my sink running again in about an hour. If I need a plumber again I would absolutely call Done Right.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bryan Burt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXRPPx2Z8-_bC76Jr3FcQcN9ug-q-z-Wq3TSi4poyAhKIvxsd-BjQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Done Right Plumbing did an excellent job replacing my main water line from my water meter to my house (~130 feet). They have advanced capabilities like horizontal drilling so they did not have to tear up my driveway or my yard/ grass (they bored underneath). The whole team (office manager, plumbers, and owner) are very professional. I got my whole water line replaced in one day and my water was back on by 4PM. I recommend Done Right for all residential and commercial plumbing needs. I was so impressed with the work and team I am recommending them to colleagues at my office.\nThank you Done Right Plumbing. You did an excellent job!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0XaFq5Ppr0Vl7t1iV7BGIF6uzGL0Qrddh4vMU_jOkcpkWIrraI-v4fLHjBrut3vf30VLlqsRa3q3wbgK-y4XTBXicb5wvx8NnMAa-EwRKLVdTbFQ2wMx6Xuq7bHGKRimQapidD=k-no"],"When":"2025-5-22"},{"Name":"Y L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIXTbspN19EYEw5ORqExJQYIi150fBe8enEBUHMFkyMLNLp1g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Over the past several years, I have received help from Steve and his team on many occasions. I have been deeply impressed 