inly for adding the cooling system. They had the most competitive package for the installing and maintenance.\n\nThomas served as the major contact. He communicated well. He provided a few options based on my home's spec and gave me fair suggestions.\n\nRecommended!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2iEoiJj-qdES2oB3G1ucFvJBOz-u2USGYbRCrVD3Rdr3TYgjZtd4wVSXUNbsfPTi8n483slALF10PdcVDyy9GtmeCYtRCmQZxG599LnqTwkzfAU8-B_jIY0PM8tqlk9kVSH3PylcyjKYcs=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-25"},{"Name":"Mark Harris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNqPIBeqpPYOmBAzgxLy7PVXu5-8dY263a-M9-XMVKej4KLIqabg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I highly recommend (and have recommended) All Climate Heating \u0026 Air Conditioning for heating and air conditioning needs. Thomas N lends a personal and professional touch to make sure customer needs are met and that all questions are answered. My Bryant one stage was impeccably installed and continues to perform well. All Climate has a terrific maintenance program and really goes the extra mile. Whether it's an emergency repair, planned maintenance, or a planned replacement, this company is wonderful to work with. Give them a try... and like me and my neighbors, I'm sure you'll be really satisfied.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dean Guo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ6Qp8mk4j-Aas8KTd_zzMut5n4Z0WKxW7Orl9trB0XLstgxw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had a furnace breakdown in Redmond and needed a full heat pump replacement. After getting several quotes, I am so glad I chose this team because Thomas provided the most fair and competitive estimates for both traditional and new heat pump systems. His knowledge of the homes in our neighborhood was critical—he knew exactly what capacity we needed, whereas others were just guessing.  Beyond the great price, their integrity is what really stood out: when the originally quoted equipment was delayed, they substituted a higher-end unit at no extra charge just to keep their promise and stay on schedule.\n\nThe heat pump installation was top-notch. Ryan, Andrew, and Antony, along with the electricians, were incredibly skilled and professional. Their quality of work was so high that even the Redmond city inspector mentioned how impressed he was with the installation.\n\nThe office support made the process seamless. Holly, Kirk, and Katie kept me updated with timely reminders and communications. Katie even went above and beyond by personally dropping off the mechanical and electrical permits at my home. That level of service is rare and truly exceeded my expectations. If you need a trustworthy HVAC team on the Eastside, look no further!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"faezeh amjadi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKTHohYRkWQQ-bEVCoZnJdhvorqXb4mpt1tsIHOq5jU93CoLQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience working with Nathan from All Climate. He was professional, knowledgeable, and very responsive from start to finish. He took the time to explain everything clearly and made sure the service was done thoroughly and efficiently.\n\nI truly appreciated his attention to detail and the care he showed while working in my home. It’s not easy to find reliable and honest service these days, but Nathan definitely exceeded my expectations.\n\nI highly recommend Nathan and the All Climate team to anyone looking for quality service. Thank you again for your help!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Byron Shutz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK24alU73GcO3fVNizLj7fqwkd2EuH-cobgOwWcMGsioUDQvA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A-C sold and installed a Bosch heat pump, exchanger \u0026 a separate air-filter unit in our home in 2023. All staff were thorough and professional throughout the process, easy to work with through the usual upgrading and site issues, and demonstrated consisting training, knowledge and customer service. Less than 3-yrs later, following the annual maintenance each year, A-C promptly responded to a service request during cold weather that resulted in A-C replacing the heat pump fan motor/blade unit, the compressor, and the compressor temperature sensor. These parts had failed under warranty. This entailed multiple hours by multiple techs and a subsequent follow-up requiring a second timely site visit. Though the parts were covered under warranty, the very substantial labor expense to replace them is not. Nonetheless, after quoting the labor costs, A-C’s Repair Manager waived the entire labor and service charges to complete the repairs and to extend the labor warranty. We are quite happy and content with A-C’s outstanding family-owned customer service – highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sherry Yee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWBF-72sBVs_0WBnmdlsLgiYDaAp6Hyd1KyXGX4fdyeFfmP7bc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had my heating and air conditioner serviced, which I was past due for. The scheduling staff were nice and professional. Nathan the technician was very pleasant. His communication was clear and well mannered. He reviewed the process before and after with his recommendations.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Frank Ma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLOnHODNFcIlbR4JmmDhYTaUaCc2sjF3FMwrirteRI3_EDxDQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Brendan did an outstanding job cleaning the ducts and dryer in my home. He was very thorough and made sure each duct was completely cleaned. He also took the time to teach me how to maintain everything on my own, which I really appreciated. Brendan went above and beyond, even doing work outside his original scope. I highly recommend him for his professionalism, quality work, and attention to detail.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eric M.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIT9t5FGOm-QnqB6SScpSr57ViaFZG78P54PjizID4_a7d9FQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Did installation of a heat pump with a furnace replacement. Reasonably priced compared to competitors, and they promptly fixed an issue with the blower fan. Professional experience throughout the process - quoting, installation, service, and billing, and I would recommend them.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
