nd myself the entire time. Quick response, with honest and knowledgeable team members, it couldn’t have gone any better. This will NOT be the last time I use this team and I highly recommend them. Can’t select both, but it was great and reasonable pricing.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vicki Clark","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLgPCVgUSy_CRV7k2GY9va3tj1DMCyL9LnmgX_49fxt1HrkIA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was referred to Osbaldo by a very happy customer - lucky me!  He was very responsive to my needs, extremely prompt, friendly, and professional service.  He is now on my speed dial!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vessie Djambazova","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJS2LLJjhSVcZDtZUCXOqVpHBOQbz0E_lP1Mh3SGQ8lBeceQQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really happy with work done by JD Plumbing\u0026 Fire Protection.\nFast and high quality work with lower end estimates.\nI highly recommend this company!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Beau Jenkins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJHm_qZT0tn-jcTcYEEp3v6leb2tKvMdjV5w0fhNXYq7YtypQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This place has the worst service I've ever experienced and over charged me by almost double the estimate. Stay clear!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"D. Eric Stephen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUktrMsK-m21H0xUf3-gx3VS9F7hubUA-lIZk3oucSgaFm5ABQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"wasnt yesterday. was this day 9.1.20 talked about work \u0026 the lack thereof","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
