","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJzMMJAddhTT_thFgPQst4_RIHiPNBw7j4ZugqGUfm7zuImIQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Was really pleased w 5 corners. Very much appreciated estimates via telephone and their pricing for buying toilets was comparable w online sites.  Installed 3 bidet toilets that we also purchased from 5 corners","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Peter Beissinger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjURaPwcB8RyYPKR9rXY-qSKchcQo4NU7j6zla-Bw_QWS640VcxI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great experience with them! Booking was straightforward and timely, and our technician, Juan, was a very pleasant guy who completed the work efficiently and without issue.\n\nThey were also very knowledgable about the details and extra requirements of the particular Toto toilet/washlets we were installing, and helped me catch a few missing pieces on my end, saving us all time and headaches. Very glad I went with them instead of some other non-Toto-Certified plumbers","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yishai Galatzer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKwWWg0R3fAb0MdfoR7WfjiUnRYYSH_Z0avG_NYNwuiV_rheg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Kenji has a phenomenal interaction with me as I was trying to figuer out which and how to install a new Toto unit in my condo.\n\nNot only he was knowledgeable, he had infinite patience, was straightforward, and guided me to a solution. By far the best interaction I ever had with a plumber/Toto expert.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Greg Braden","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLNEYzMtlCOo9A4FlulpiA7Iy8qHx1lVBNx6V9-jsPbCoV9VA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Overall: great and fast service, transparent pricing, plumbers had great \"bedside manner\" and did not try upselling or hard selling.  We had a leaky toilet and 5 corner's owner gave very fast response to my email query for repair or replace options.  I had an interest in replacing the faulty toilet with a new super-efficient Toto, and the owner helped me choose the best model for our needs, likewise I purchased the new Toto through 5 corners and they gave as good a price as you could find anywhere on the web; likewise labor costs were as good as or slightly better than other Seattle plumbers.  5 corners got the new toilet in 1 day and immediately worked with me to schedule an install just a day or two after that.  Scheduling window was precise (not +/- 3 hours etc.) and installer showed up exactly on time.  Removal of old toilet and installation of new one was smooth and took less than 2 hours.  Communication very good throughtout.  Overall great process/service and I recommend to others.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tula Holmes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWRAMBQH39AdO_nem7CXDch3yI_WDg2hhMBp-oNtYzJWOumA3n7=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"5 Corners Plumbing is the best! They were prompt, did a professional and thorough job, cleaned up everything and when they left, I had the exact toilet that I wanted with no muss or fuss! THANK YOU 5 Corners Plumbing!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Richard Nakamoto","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMWsTmmm_9UAD2rdOPMjas4ob8pIpjJU6JzhvIEr-cuIBDPE4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am very happy with the professional yet friendly service provided by 5 Corners Plumbing LLC.  I will be calling them very soon to do additional work around the house.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Leonard Fusselman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUzgwI1iDGwJB2sIaS584KAfnNWoeqbvIx3Q7YV5adwUhHBzCN6=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Emailed me immediately over the weekend and gave me a quote.  Showed up, did the work, and the final price was close to the quote. Great company","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":n