.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIyhcbgoLQfC8HRrcpc9FHp-knMeorEFUfV8nBXq_UwL5HWQA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I called Private I plumbing for a water heater replacement and was impressed by their punctuality, reliability and friendliness. The plumber arrived on time, explained everything clearly, and completed the job efficiently. I felt they were trustworthy and the price was fair. Would definitely use them again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Steven Roberts","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJTkXKu3IxxDtyCzEdu-ns0hqSljngdpA6ICKLbo7cmoUZPaw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I called Private I Plumbing when my water heater was not venting. It was filling the house with exhaust. He was very concerned and they were at my house in under an hour. He worked for a while to fix the problem. He was very knowledgeable and discussed our options.. The plumber was professional, honest about what needed to be done. He did everything we asked which included an extra job. I appreciated the punctuality and the reliable service – no hidden costs and everything was explained clearly. Highly recommend for any residential plumbing needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"J Mc","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLiGH7ngcCcqr5TzW5WZ9z09lXeId3Jz18BDmGKBidK3laY4w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I called Private I Plumbing to get an estimate for a new hot water tank, and Mark came out right away. From the start, he was friendly, honest, and easy to work with. While he was here, I showed him a few other plumbing issues around the house, and he took the time to walk through everything and add it to the estimate without any pressure.\n\nMark ended up installing a tankless hot water heater, adding nine new shutoff valves to toilets and sinks, fixing an outdoor faucet, replacing two toilets, installing a new garbage disposal, and repairing the pipes under our kitchen sink. He made the entire process simple and stress-free, and the quality of his work really shows.\n\nWe were so impressed that we already plan to have him back to install a utility sink in our garage. Mark does excellent work, charges fair prices, and is far more affordable than the big plumbing companies you see advertised on TV. I highly recommend Private I Plumbing if you’re looking for someone reliable who truly cares about doing the job right","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Blake Jorgensen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJNdNqccmreDnvZq1Fxa2xtUPwPLoFL88ShiQReMl0p843E4Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"5/5 stars – each star for customer care, product quality, atmosphere, speed, and value. The plumber arrived right on time, was professional and honest about the issue, and fixed the problem quickly and efficiently. Their speed, punctuality, and clear communication impressed me. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hansen Z","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVLz0-8rSYidEuXuU7Ucrk4GbL5jjjSDSvdYOeQ2dBNEaee-mdK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Mark is one of the best plumber I have ever seen, he is able to get things done with quality, and the price is always reasonable.\nI have asked the help from Mark multiple times, he never disappoints me.Apart from that, Mark is very friendly, I like to work with Mark whenever I can.\n\nPlease trust this private plumbing llc👍","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lilli","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWw3T1CTCWWAQEfVlSa4JPra-KsETvcXrQN6cIfERaZc7WjPyw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Mark was great! Very prompt and knowledgeable","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kananu Kananu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJSkQBzflkuxlDeMv7DN_REWsmkbzUKql4SZeNCteszw4IXCA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very knowledgeable in his trade. Good value for money.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_re