edkmyte2Q2F48NBHIHM_yEA6jUp1jsg8czoMbs36ImEgHBMj9xuIXb-49jFOUPyqXTgvAmSUUhjMBCX_0q6AXkvpYC6=k-no"],"When":"2026-4-20"},{"Name":"Patrick Malone","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLVVr1w6Wd8OkpxD5fOG2CFHs5a1kViGdYmiTNSk4i5F-lO-g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"True professionals. This is a company you can count on!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alena Nieves","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXKKyypDMxvG_W2euBVm01KfAWmjhBP51dpVRCKc8oEPz2nDkF1Qg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have used Levi for several of our plumbing projects. Updating our water heater, valve replacement (inside the walls) replacement of shower/tub fixtures. I can always trust Levi’s integrity \u0026 customer care.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2ynbiukPkpJWtBrCAPXR8XpgevBNxVymrhs_SrwwNK0bPQlH-8Oj9HOQ7gX2kxsdbMjRuD3YrjhKFxnUJO2G8fd7Ui5RY-jDILhLLiCe7NjSGZCQ2iO6WhjHhozCsjV8x6_g7z22iY49U4=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0Sh8OV-8N_KIG03SEhheKVM78Np9YHWoTth96ongrPv7uO72UXw5TCwr2QgUDb1ttN_X7l2hEDOnGonvgjQ4gaEm4SLlevC0caRw_uxzzAHCdE7tOek6KHr6LlkLxU2MOG92g63D0tYFM=k-no"],"When":"2026-4-18"},{"Name":"Brian Eichelberger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLiZlKx0NkHveARyWutHF0v6d6JpuT1clbjeBN6_00yD2n-vQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Levi is my Go-To Pro with plumbing projects. He is knowledgable and down to earth - he actually helps me understand my issues and learn about how I can take care of my system!\n\nHe has helped me with an outdoor tankless water heater install, kitchen plumbing, and a bathroom/laundry retrofit and install. Highly recommended!!!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Benjamin Hosaflook","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVH4VO2sd5Zh-gKIAtogNXco5VoQ6WlI3GQ8dGsJGbxmMYZMnfnOg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great service with great transparency and work ethic!\n\nI had a great experience with Pax Consultations. Levi is Super easy to communicate with from the start—quick responses, clear explanations. You're getting transparency in terms of what's needed vs what's nice to have without it being jammed down your throat. Family run \u0026 operated so there's no extra fluff that comes with big companies. You can tell he takes pride in what he does and actually cares about doing things the right way. Would definitely recommend to anyone needing reliable plumbing work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Deborah Torah","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWuloo_7n7IYr_VwQH30h8sA8B8yCGG_oYKhWczhuDdaNuXEPU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a truly outstanding experience with Pax Home Consultations, and I can’t recommend them highly enough—especially if you’re unsure where to start with a plumbing issue.\n\nWhat sets Pax Home Consultations apart is the value and quality of their consultation. From the very beginning, it was clear this wasn’t just a quick visit—it was a thoughtful, thorough evaluation designed to give me real clarity and peace of mind. They took the time to understand my concerns, walk through my options, and explain everything in a way that felt honest and pressure-free. That level of care made the consultation feel not just helpful, but absolutely necessary.\n\nLevi, who came out, was exceptional. He was professional, knowledgeable, and incredibly efficient, but what stood out most was his calm and respectful approach. He made sure I felt comfortable and informed every step of the way, which is something you don’t always find.\n\nWhen it came time to move forward with the work, I felt completely confident because of that strong foundation the consultation provided. The entire experience—from start to finish—was handled with professionalism and attention to detail, and the work itself addressed some very important needs in my home.\n\nIf you’re considering Pax Home Consultations, don’t skip the consultation—it’s truly where they shine. They bring not only expertise, but also a sense of reassurance that you’re making the right decisions for your home.\n\nI wouldn’t hesitate to call them again.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1OoRxE6tpm4xc0c4RmJMWq6oVQjfaWQ0oDm3PXkS9LvXbPJRKYj_wLM5zXVNinQQyOTzCHPvSEQL2kmEEZiOLBSN_qynL2lBKecmFYGaxuTMSxdn2ZILFPR0hP7whkF3Ng_x6Qo6HmeUNa=k-no"],"When":"2026-4-17"},{"Name":"Pax Home Consultations","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU6dFKHf3ZuKqB-R3-pqigvnRRZUjK5e1N929qgb4Rds0bN_KY6yg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a consultation and it went great! I understand my plumbing more and I know what to do about my water heater. Thanks!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2jvfR_DKZBsdRpAXMm4y8KnQmIwsxj8cyqry1z2i6w5KsH-NRP8YSQKmsUSTmFQDxRkMZZBbTa16v6DjG7tOo1owj5QmHh-FxhECitgcbd3muBMnmiziHA8l2qVS4ElUTXYwDAPMc20IlG=k-no"],"When":"2026-4-17"}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
