orner. In addition, the ceiling repair was completed so seamlessly that it blends perfectly with the rest of the ceiling, making it impossible to tell there had ever been damage. Ruslan and his team were also very flexible in working around our schedules, and he checked in on the project’s progress each day to ensure everything stayed on track.\n\nWe had multiple questions throughout the project, and Ruslan was always easy to reach and quick to reply. His communication made the entire process feel smooth and well‑managed. Pricing was also very competitive compared to two other quotes we received from other remodelers\n\nOverall, working with Ruslan and his team was a great experience. Their professionalism, craftsmanship, flexibility, and responsiveness made a stressful situation much easier, and we would highly recommend them for any bathroom remodel or repair.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dung Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUw0nLZQKr2H-JRlGMNZBuPfejkJpHtBRc14TMG3JXu4ev7FIs0xA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Ruslan came out and gave me a very reasonable estimate for my bathroom remodeling project. He and his crew worked efficiently and completed the job in just over a week. It helped that the property was vacant. Overall, I’m satisfied with the results. There were a few cosmetic issues I noticed during the project, and Ruslan was happy to fix them. One downside was that a sliding shower door was ordered by mistake—my preference was a pivot door, but by the time we realized it, it was too late to change. I’m giving Ruslan and his team four stars.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Piyush","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJNfXnmgbCWEtB88AVv0hd1u3qnaXQKUTIFKGVKEE7cBLnjIMUE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ruslan and his crew beautifully remodeled our half bath and converted it to a full bath in under two weeks. They did an great job! Ruslan is very responsive and kept