scription":"Vik and his team came and replaced three toilets and repaired a faulty replacement we had done to a fourth toilet.  They were fast, efficient, and hauled always all old fixtures and trash when they were done.  I was able to book them with 24 hours notice.  Would absolutely use them again - great experience overall.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mukul Kumar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUGuBzanMoDa5i5cmHpqtbIPtxGglCqa9NIWQHR-YlEXSnR8y-P7w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was initially hesitant about hiring a handyman for my cooktop installation, but I'm so glad I chose Vik Home Service. Viktor and Dimitri were absolutely fantastic! They were punctual, professional, and incredibly knowledgeable. Viktor's engineering background was a huge plus, and he explained everything clearly and patiently.\n\nNot only did they install my new cooktop perfectly, but they also took the time to repair my old one, which I was able to sell for a decent price. They were very thorough and made sure everything was safe and up to code before leaving. I couldn't be happier with the service I received from Vik Home Service, and I would highly recommend them to anyone in need of a reliable and skilled handyman.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Loretta Weimer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJWxIF3Oe-CG11hubT55yut_r8ZqRs4TgYna5oEJrbPmbZ5uer_A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We chose Vik Home Service to remove \u0026 replace 3 toilets. I purchased the units from Lowe's and then when Vik arrived they went to work and first thing the first unit was brokenin the box. This was my mistake because the box had been opened and returned i did't know. I returned to Lowe's and got another and it also turned out to have been opened and was broken. I went back to Lowe's and finally got a unit that I was assured was new. Long story but thanks to Vik we finally had them installed. I highly reccommed Vik Home Service, the did an exceptional job and cleaned up after.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eric Sun","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU03oy9C40YYlxZKizV4r6BQxWdFboFQ6USMFFciLhz9xCnfdw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Working with Vik and his son was an absolute pleasure. I recently had a clogged sink drain and reached out to them for help. They exceeded my expectations by promptly arriving on-site the same day and swiftly resolving the issue. Their level of care and attention to detail during the job was remarkable, and they left the area spotless once they were finished. I highly recommend their services and would gladly work with them again in the future. Thank you for the exceptional service!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ux El","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXNX9xWejz7BUXUqCLB5HeTpiN9pbb63lqfNIDztWNfO2NAFD1T=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Vik and his son form an excellent team. They are efficient, accurate, and gets job done with less time and less cost. They pay attention to details, wipe everything clean, and even replaced the broken seals on my drain pipes for free. I would hire these guys again at any time.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
