. Their team consistently delivers high-quality workmanship that we can depend on. We appreciate their fair and reliable pricing, as well as their commitment to meeting our project schedules.\n\nWhen an issue does arise, Prokash Plumbing is always prompt to respond and resolves matters quickly and professionally, giving us complete peace of mind. Their reliability and dedication make them an essential partner in the success of our projects.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1jykq8U-3mCg7gC5ePgqolIhErMVGRBbElQfMwfDv9ehu0hEJzFMLX_MnlWL4P9cGEcfI6g7d9v--xQ_v2n5RbprZ2OyvddrWbXiVXIlpUyhYglGbzirhlIsgM2ODRmxOW19gWsQU6yAqH=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1scLplWZiODU1yaLQq7TwtIBXgYm7XvVB8y1eA24YqpJ-Dnz_N8-0xxtGHIa4ri19AmfwZRHSoc3inAo8qXqJ3utAKG9kk--aj6s21tFHB4t99wmXDr_g0dTh2naWxQVMvjDszpThPiYi3=k-no"],"When":"2025-9-11"},{"Name":"Ankit","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWM_u4_kSI3a2YWmvXfkreZHbu8yEz9TDLBNMonb3zomn3yYwjSzA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We hired Gary Prokash Plumbing for fire sprinkler repair work following tree damage to our home. The quality of their work was excellent, the installation team was professional, thorough, and the system passed all inspections without issues.\n\nJuan Carlos, our project manager, was responsive throughout the project and coordinated well with our general contractor. There was a communication challenge late in the project regarding potential additional work on older sprinkler components. However, when we raised concerns about the timing of this recommendation, Juan worked directly with our contractor to resolve it fairly and professionally.\n\nWhat impressed me most was their willingness to make things right when there was a misunderstanding. Rather than getting defensive, they found a solution that worked for everyone. This kind of customer service and integrity is rare in the construction industry.\n\nThe craftsmanship was solid, inspections passed on schedule, and they stood behind their work. I'd recommend Gary Prokash Plumbing for fire sprinkler projects, and I appreciate Juan's professionalism in handling both the technical work and the occasional bumps that come up in any remodel project.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ahmad Hassan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUntgPnnxJ8mGLtXswllhbTQVBw2lGh8UBcFDjjsmVl9WB2vJYX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Gary Prokash Plumbing \u0026 Fire Sprinkler did an excellent job on our sprinkler system work. The team was professional, knowledgeable, and efficient throughout the project. Jaun, who handled my case, was a great communicator—very responsive, clear, and easy to work with. Everything was handled smoothly and professionally. I would highly recommend them for fire sprinkler services.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"carlos marroquin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWvzOd_pADFyeGnCmyCOFXvo77QXo1jTGNo-VjrwwtSdpyWdGGcjQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an outstanding experience with Gary Prokash Plumbing! David and Manuel did exceptional work at my home. They installed an on-demand recirculating pump (AutoHot) that eliminated the wait time for hot water in my most remote bathroom shower—such a game changer! Not only is it more convenient, but I’ve already noticed a reduction in my monthly utility bill.\n\nThey also replaced a rusty pressure-reducing valve at the water main and a new pressure gauge. Their attention to detail and professionalism stood out. They were prompt, knowledgeable, and respectful of my home throughout the entire process.\n\nHighly recommend Gary Prokash Plumbing for anyone looking for top-notch plumbing service done right the first time!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2K7QmTPNJOTU6FTBmR4r5GuTYWrDNmq-d6LJMYPzDeurfXBKpCNIi3G9c4UjIfUUCpHruM4EWMuWf-87LaNZh3KX2JlRBINTlL19l6WgY16ul418tv95n6A3iJUdjN4au53d