den","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUYmBVOWisSJDI_6-cyUxu_Pdc9LCSZX8SV8xwIswyZeyuoeCk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They fixed my problems up really quickly; was very professional while still communicating. I won’t get into details what the job was, but it would’ve cost me a lot more than the other plumbers around Seattle. Absolutely recommend, Lance was very very helpful in explaining everything in a timely manner.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cutter Werdel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9SMGlKrRVEmFzf0K2aduFTKjcjmsBsbMVg_rSA59KrRtzGBs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you need any assistance with Plumbing and Heating then A Game is the best place to help you. I cannot thank Lance enough for his help. He is one of the most genuine, kind, and honest people you will ever meet. He will tell you exactly what you need to hear, not what you want to and he makes sure he puts in the time and effort it takes to make sure your problem is completely solved. He cares so much about his customers and team, and it shows in his work. Thank you again Lance for all your help.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Darci Evidon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLFRuNJyhwVMqCC2YlESsPjb-mcnWFCu4cWfVdI-v0GWqRgiWA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really pleased with the service I received today! Had a leaking/rotted old galvanized pipe in my dirty crawl space. Lance the owner and crew showed up in a day and guided me as to my choices to fix without any pressure as to whether to fix just the broken joint or all of the pipe. Super nice and respectful guys. Quickly got into the wet unpleasant crawl space and got the plumbing work done for a reasonable price. Very impressed, would definitely recommend them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Curt Rutland","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVKbwBDb2rYczSXj85pXvLHogLZ1MmzTjGz6HajCMV5df304Xfw3g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lance is a total professional and he helped repair a broken and leaky main water line shut off valve in a really old house THE NEXT DAY. The prior setup was ineffective and wasted space (look at the before and after photos!) and Lance recommended a much cleaner and more reliable solution on site within the originally quoted price. He and his team worked fast and professionally to get the job done right without any issues or need for a call back. I will definitely call them first the next time I have any plumbing needs. 10/10 would recommend to a friend.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn07dS6hpvWT6r1Y3ToSOD5T6Z8KiWDDmAVbsV4HYZlrtAC5xSPbzjwLkQ7tvK8OLCeaqEGdK0DYe88TkKWohLaGUt4rIEBrzog6L6pWx-T9U7QrqjdYl1oUJ49s2zu-Vp3ucVz9x5uG1-4P=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3EaVBeoaQOr_lul3PBUcunXh1qw6ONgmdaJJjY-YUCCO-oIcXa52m49qJiGSKRGPH9x2gAxJ_gFTftZHDmNPumJudcen2KOVJ4VU44isbl-zsFUq7Ye-IJdyZcGV2DlJOF37ZjMsxFrQzU=k-no"],"When":"2025-8-2"},{"Name":"Eric Dunn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWbebFCPp6j6KKJi2TFssImoikNdJrOwOKUMSRUPAE5jiZqQCo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a sewer discharge pump replaced. Quick and efficient work. Called on a sunday night and was able to be serviced next day. Very professional and got the job done fast.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"David Wu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ5ltks2ckgGG82zVHBogLCGVAGE--AupqLpSgT9rMCXUP4SQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great team; great communication; transparent pricing, quick service!!  What more can I say?  I enjoyed meeting Dan and Toby who met w/ me and took care of my project (install 2 toilets). Ahead of the work, Lance was great with straightforward communication and help with coordinating scheduling. Very appreciative of this team!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Daniel Webbon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLMFcJflXvo_ZayKlCaWH67vupijS2amGYCq-HYBCXRMetJFQ0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lance and his apprentice did a wonderful job on a tricky install. They explained the issues to me very clearly and gave me their expert advice on the best way to proceed. The new sink looks great and functions as it should. Honest, friendly, and competent. Can’t ask for more than that.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
