Ip5ZcASxM5r7g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Steve and his team took great care of me and my flood situation. They were responsive, professional and very helpful working with my insurance company.  Wouldn't hesitate to use them again!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kelli","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU-Se0DQia84DY8Y0SUNPaADeo5-BZfqzt9awuCHoUAigLKLbI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Kainan (Crew Lead) did an amazing job with navigating through a difficult and stressful incident involving a upstairs toilet overflow. Everything was communicated well, quickly, and with empathy for my situation. Work was also done professionally and with respect for this being my home. While I wish the situation had never happened, I am very grateful I chose Servpro of Redmond to do the water mitigation. Also thankful to Tim (Operations Manager) for assisting through the insurance estimate, service engagement, and more than one follow up call along the way.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Denisse H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIsi_0KTnmP13Yw-i3CiUu0uURdSUKw5cdgdHfCWKxEpqJ0hA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"From the very beginning this company was professional and reliable, starting out with Jimmy getting the estimate ready.  After that Kainan came and did an amazing job at my place, not only he kept things nice and neat, but he was always available to answer all my questions.  He truly cared about my situation and spent time educating me about the process, I felt heard and understood.  He was professional and very knowledgeable. When it was the time to remove the equipment he made sure to leave the place spotless, I highly recommend them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"OutB1rding","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLzFL5Er3AODWtdUE0ehfxLQO4fcjBPLmOoY9T_ARQjWlxYPsM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jimmy led Cayden and team t