Name":"Justin Gilbert","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKWTOBvTGfEqeX5P03i6-mPfsyjh216fCaxVrs8LV7FntqGhQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had recently bought a house built in the '20s. Within the first few months, my sewer backed up and I thought it was going to cost an arm and a leg. I got a couple quotes and they seemed pretty high. I called Wezee's and their price seemed fair, they got me scheduled within a couple days and got her done. I was not a fan of having my whole driveway dug up but they finished quickly and were very professional and polite the whole way. I've used them since then for a faucet install, new toilet - they are my go to plumbing company and I prefer them to the bigger companies. They save me money and they're honest.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Wes Schneider","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUt6MSLiFkVlkhtYJIj3k8rXKkXBcCqokdR16ZQCkbG601MBeZm=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We've used Wezee's multiple times now, and they've been fantastic. They've always made it out swiftly, diagnosed the source of our plumbing issues, and helped us make choices that solve our current situation and look ahead to prevent future issues. We've worked with Dan several times, and he's always given us clear, mindful advice on top of doing great work. Jennifer in the office has also always been quick and clear with organizing jobs and working with our schedules. Overall, we couldn't be more pleased, and we've recommended them to several friends.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"J Von Stratton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMQNnQd5Y41mFtA3lWegyz-53TZs-6BddyePRNS-KJiUK92pb8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Worked with Wezee's twice now. They hooked up our new bathroom, and replaced a water heater a few years ago. They also helped me a few times when the disposal was jammed, and talked me through how to fix it. Will 100% ring them again when I need plumbing services.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0SQvSr6y9wrhnuLX4-r54sjpwxgo1ooUUAucf4-S9TauTZW867B79nJaoJcHvHADGe3AJRqst3-IEs8JUGTW5xTA4aFtTSc8fna6ADMvm9W0zSrA7DpTQOt4C_HwOS81F_j4gG=k-no"],"When":"2021-2-6"},{"Name":"Mary FORTINO","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUpKw0ie5YDtCc00gYb3KISrC9cR7VAAgT2qdbelQ3UZhoR6To=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Holiday weekend sink back up and leak. Called at 2 pm and Josh arrived right on time at 4 pm. He was knowledgeable and professional. Had the sink running in no time. The charge was affordable. So pleased. Wezes was recommended to me by another plumber (Cody). He told me: good people, solid company, fair price and quality service. I completely agree.  I will definitely recommend them to friends and family.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eleni Adams","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUrZJzjOsOAUarAou7WBl7yIRzH1OBlWm5CKoyXwSGz5sg_l1Du=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wezee's was very communicative and responsive throughout the process of our water line replacement. They were reasonable and charged exactly what was quoted. Zack did great work and even offered to replace our kitchen faucet for free. We felt like we were in good hands I wouldn't hesitate to use them again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bob Silverstein","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXrlZJTUQVHM9oc6lzw6acAsvj0O0LRXklXRt3uMYmbVwvOzf3o=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had Dan come over and do some repairs in our bathroom. He gave us a very detailed analysis of what the problems were, what options we had, and also gave a recommendation about the most cost-effective approach to handling some of our issues, given that we're in an older home. He also gave us an estimate on some larger plumbing updates. I found his work to be fairly priced and high quality, and his bid for the larger job (which we have not proceeded with yet) was also reasonable. I would definitely recommend Wezee's. They are responsive, and I don't feel like they're the kind of company that will use scare tactics to upsell you on repairs or service that are not needed (and that is definitely not the case with some other companies we've got quotes from).","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michael Soules","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJiN9eU-5UP_ZD-2GhodGg1KBOjDqQbCOlKX3wgyq9wp8ep7g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dustin and Ronnie removed our old plastic main water shut off valve And replaced it with a new bronze valve. It took some expertise to configure the PVC parts to match the gap in our main waterline. They were quick and efficient and cleaned up after themselves. Good work.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
