ut and pinpoint the location of the leak, which I did. Topgun plumbing provided a very competitive and reasonable price bid to repair the leak which was under an asphalt driveway. They completed the repair in less than a full day. They arrived on time and the cost was exactly what was quoted.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0nT72fm0iVXd0qadv41FSr9nOdYn3Mvk6DrKWl4J5lSEaUfFLrHE8SKt6OdHCr5FAr7FEy8xtGwR7Iuoy7H5g7bkVIXT3PVTz2N2FX3tUWfnaWdjDCw8enHxM5jdqTb-MmBxrk=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0sj1gsMfUTip2k7k4jRUllvB4rzPu3KGwsZ1s5UiI8VIuAv5Evun7N43_tL79pxzJfW6fbnfylHelzK5HN_5XQ7Di3WCTZQkZhcODQhZE75miUXjiD2B8tJPwxO7An9q5LKRqbXA=k-no"],"When":"2024-8-22"},{"Name":"Edmund Tee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVqz5mfsRnHRdgKc9D4ycgju_7exrdFthE4CnmlS_3xqKF2fj0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Plumbers that are professional, punctual, proficient, polite and pleasant. Can’t ask for more.\n\nI was impressed by both Jake and Greg, and the way they extracted that large rock that had crushed our waterline through the decades we have lived here.\n\nI did do a double take at first at the price when presented with the estimate before the job, but that’s more a reflection of the inflationary times we live in than TopGun’s prices itself.\n\nIt is what it is, and I appreciated Jake taking a couple of hundred off in recognition of me done a chunk of digging to locate the leak.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2_nG8XiNGP2rZ8PesirtzmJpYYA27jWmKL9dVia-rvWl5aGPxJxxCjr7-Lk3YzSSHKRdKxY3k0NrgheM1X8jUycQzDkBAoN9lfRiWvupLlsbDApqzFwn_qapNzDKhPYH77oz3d=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0wborsLLJx_-f9y4KAPRPT-TgQpIc1HHu8VgdKp6HAzMhDlz0PF_cVAYba0tCW2NACWZkUIEgcCUOH9vylbMdegczPLWzVzWG08Hh4hGNih-3nTdnSt-9IPqrKz1d3JkddPFgKTA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn383zxjODR1qfDu8C0RSesNwnhP8OyYrAugJpjU367ahQISoZmxCbfKFxLqPDTJIa0VwdY6xm0hLj34bWzwjzK2Wdn40gM4gC5O6USugUgud-Gzf_rz96YElND6gdW9e-80KTgW=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn37EPQ7QQFcpSUN6KOWdotPpj2lKNa8rCHULNkY0kCL7qzoSEUCB1yUuYruFfBDqaGWso_OC1KHuuh2wX0zQ8i3w98IU0q0NbyDpd3xDsWvPjWgq0LWVTwbV--YkvZ-zTlbFaCDSA=k-no"],"When":"2024-6-24"},{"Name":"J D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIBCNCgSjVO5IbtUJkPTjiHmg7C0z6QMptltgG1qJkbx9Ktwx2P=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They're the best! Yes, believe the high rating.  We had an urgent issue with a pipe breakage in front yard.  Out of many calls they're the only one who responded, AND delivered as they promised.  Even the timing of when someone would show up was spot on.\n\n\"Jake from Topgun\" went above and beyond and fixed the issue pristinely and explained everything well.  It's easy to tell that they take the quality and trustworthiness of their job seriously.\n\nThank you team and 'Jake from Topgun' :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dani H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXtSGXXsBlvaxyCuaLx2j9aeg--9ZrVwlIDz8x6-DNFb04DQrQXeA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a main water line leak and I got many quotes for the water line replacement. Topgun was by far the best price for this job. They have all of their own equipment, no sub contacting like other companies. They completed the work in one day with no disturbance to the driveway. They are very friendly and knowledgeable and I will definitely use them for any future plumbing issues we may have.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Scott Holcomb","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIUuCWdkapUsKKzzL3AHbP4KNKLohwxA_6nMQ4AAtcc22hSgQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Replacing a water main is a difficult choice, a difficult job.  I am glad I asked Topgun Plumbing to do the job and they sent their best team Jake and Greg to do the job using the best materials.  Their professionalism, knowledge, efficiency and respect for property and neighbors made this experience a very positive one for me, I have no regrets!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"David Lim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJS1qrK6uPWaZP8mzKJxb8eGVA_gUXcXB_lDD_tGTmNYty4iIaZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"TLDR; I had a great experience with Topgun, and you should call Topgun for excellent service, honest work, and fair prices.\n\nI had a leak in the ceiling. I called Topgun, the call taker was polite and courteous. Within minutes, I got a call back from the owner Al, who said he could stop by and look on the same  day.\n\nTopgun team member Eric showed up shortly after and root caused the problem to a bad shower drain seal. The Topgun team, including Eric, Al and Josh all showed up and worked together quickly to solve the problem on the same day. The team was very polite and professional, which left me with no doubt they would do a great job. Topgun solved the leak problem in a timely and cost effective manner.\n\nI’m extremely satisfied with the Topgun’s work and the positive results. They charged a very fair price and I will definitely call Topgun first if I have any future plumbing issues. I’d recommend Topgun to my friends and family.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rob Slabaugh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLo6WIxYO0CW7cdY8tHfMhgwxm5jC-b0KJ_jkuSrJVZ28aoAA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Topgun Plumbing took care of our leak promptly and fairly.  Next day service, price as quoted.  I highly recommend this company.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
