 pricing and itemized everything down to the permits, extra wire routing for replacing our old thermostat with a nest!\n2. Dean clearly explain the difference different options. Between a Mitshibishi Heat Pump and Heat Pump/Furnace and Furnace/AC, we were able to find out Furnace/AC was most reliable and economical for us since we have a backup gas powered electricity generator that would pair well with a Furnace, and since we were only using the AC for a few weeks a year, we didn't need a heat pump. We got the right tiers of items for our needs: top of line furnace and an efficient but not over the top AC.\n3. It's winter now and our Bryant furnace is keeps the temperature much more stable instead of big up and downs from our old furnace. It's also much more quieter. Our house feels so much better with the heat stabilization which also helps with moisture levels!\n4. Our air filters are winners! My wife could immediately tell the difference. REME-LED is non-invasive UV filter. The Honeywell is the most efficient for not reducing airflow vs MERV filter and while my wife is pregnant we didn't want risk of ozones associated with any electric filter even though it's minimal so we turn off our Honeywell. Dean made it right for us by finding us eight MERV 13 filters to last us 2 whole years for this pregnancy and another one if needed. Thanks to Dean for going above and beyond for us.\n5. The install crew Nick and Maxime rocked! They were respectful to wear coverings on their boots, fast, and did great work on the install as we had to route our AC coolant line further away behind our garage since we didn't have space to put it right next to our house.\n6. We quoted 4 HVAC companies and Alexander's had the best price for quality.\n\n100% Recommend Alexander's Heating \u0026 Air Conditioning!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3mUqeYkqTM41Vm9nbKqJFIkhrjfvkeSDtiWaceZpNU4gZPS0sBk63O2SukI3yzTRsbcijNm2zsC8yut68icpXsCr1FO9hD4dYoyKM1LrQnYLsv_tBvGR9wyzkkhV12KJ1VHeu5Jp382D3N=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn36brezxCcBA2Fg-pSYRPhReKWR0cv28BbOfdAMmSn5LdGJ0wMMgr0bGaC-EaDe5hRpBfcl5vX3iySfFvuN8JyjFbZT_I9i4B0VMYnc3oZLbyy2zOdowxZlI5PsDZbsC41pjCMkuYW9AltB=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn17NCXe1BmiqaJ36gQxA-ppSTXoyw0ZrC-7vUUdyqUOSgGtKVkzVEHLqgtpraH1XAStvpDpanKlAShAPa91_3N7OzsIrlHHBj0W2BXnQx8_o0VeT5YIaWWGCOZnsfSeploOT4qEkYtpCNkJ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3IGz18R7Dc8jxTG6DcFaTYGgI8FLvVZihlEFMETuyejg0qS9Emuf4AqzryE5J8sYIsmoJ9VO4fq54C7OOp3uC_xgksVUi4koSTH6i214Smu6gWgSaOFaUEyuaAdADqxkovwUjtVGHCVd0=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1G1qbva5JY_sckSwJ5TXECHag9tMIvlx-Mvm8a_Fmrj6h4M4Aeq8i-rAIMxamZRtoU6OUOid3UT0O0u_JuLe7WRlJOzUt6QnAaXO13hpNmcegn61rbpemXXVSDzW6lOYMfMzRDwOFFarRI=k-no"],"When":"2025-11-14"},{"Name":"Val Z","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJXjC_ZoU-ahONDi_lIVLx0rLIXWaZbxG5pyEcWoP-3FNUvDw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I can’t recommend Alexander’s Heating \u0026 Air Conditioning highly enough. Alexander, the owner, is incredibly responsive, understanding, and extremely professional. He has a wonderful attitude and truly cares about his customers, which made a stressful situation so much easier.\nWe came home from vacation to find the temperature inside our house was 46°F, with below-freezing temperatures outside, and we needed help immediately. Alexander and his team showed up right at 7:30 am to make sure our home was warm as quickly as possible — that level of promptness is rare and deeply appreciated.\nHis team was very punctual, professional, and pleasant to work with. They took the time to explain everything clearly, answered all of our questions, and made sure we were comfortable with the entire process.\nOn top of the excellent service, the price was the best compared to several other companies we contacted for estimates.\nExceptional service, fair pricing, and true professionalism from start to finish. Excellent experience all around!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gwen Leino","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL28VV1bh4vVTAoVrPvnmWQmpT4OFHU-BQwUY0Np2DytPv452s=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had our water heater, Air conditioning unit and furnace installed by Alexander's heating during the pandemic. Today, we had our furnace serviced. Justin was great and took the time to show us a few tricks to program our thermostat and modify the outdoor air return so that we didn't get blasted with cold air throughout the day. He was very kind and personable and showed up right on time. A great home maintenance experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"James Clements","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX0U3AEdXuC7zlqi16e55BP_W_w3gxPDAJk8RxzZ5hbFlU2C2c=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Purchased a heat pump from Alexander's in August.  Couldn't be more pleased with the experience.  Dean did an awesome job checking out our home, explaining our options, and making recommendations.  Gave us a very competitive quote, on par with Costco's vendor.  Guys that did the install (Nick and his partner) did a knock out job.  Roughly 3 months later, have had no issues with cooling or heating.  Elena was great to work with, too.  Good people.  Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ray Maxwell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXXMkjzOSsUEFYKhbrqg2mrehLvyQsd2YE9XgtMTOi2YSnln0k=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The two installers were very professional and got my new heat pump and furnace up and running in a timely manner. They left the garage very tidy after they finished. Alexander’s helped me in the past when Bob’s heating said they would no longer support my AC unit on a hot day. Because of that, I decided to reward them with my business for the new equipment. My sister works for a custom builder that uses Alexander’s and she recommended them to me.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Meredith Rasche","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWsKq1iSkZopIRsFOXYxY5eruUrhql0WFZIoj732_uVJG4xgBbz=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Alexander’s Heating has been a fantastic company to work with.  We have used them on some very complex and extensive residential projects.  They are on time and communicative.  Would highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kevin Rhoades","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUscYC2qrTcq-NfkL1Oou71bElBhNhkGuZdg_RQ5Mq9OH56GEU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Alexander’s did a great job installing a Mitsubishi multi-zone heat pump system. Their team worked hard to get it installed quickly despite near freezing temperatures. Highly recommend Alexander’s.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"henry Safi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI3boagTcKeX2Pclpgp1HKyqrLndpd9XF1tqE9a7Y1srE8sCA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Justin from Alexander Heating did a great job diagnosing the issue with our newly installed furnace heater and adjusting the airflow to address the problem. He was thorough, knowledgeable, and took the time to make sure everything was set up correctly. Scott followed up to replace the limit switch, which we really appreciated. Both were professional and attentive, and they made sure everything was working as expected. Highly recommend Alexander Heating and their team.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
