m came promptly on time and James and Victor did the install.  Very polite careful and conscientious people who did the install right the first time.  Everything per code, clean and professional work.  Great close out instructions, paperwork and very clean garage.  I’ll say this about Pearce and the people from the front desk to the installers.   They are a 5 star plus company with great leadership at the top. A dependable company that can be trusted.  I’m a retired architect with both construction and building permitting experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jennifer Spindel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV_uev5_IwuBCJBBCttIPTPI1fEZGRQCYNWbxxWUwctnwuuiiuK=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a fantastic team! Claire, James, Pete and Victor did an incredible job installing our new heat pump this week. From start to finish, the experience was seamless. Their pricing was very fair and transparent and the value for the level of service we received was outstanding.  Claire was knowledgeable and honest, making the initial process easy. James led the crew with great efficiency, finishing the project in just two days instead of the estimated three, and Pete and Victor were very skillful, as well as considerate of our pets. The team left the workspace impeccably clean each day. I highly recommend Pearce for any HVAC needs.  You’ll be in great hands!\"","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Faraz Qadri","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVw-AvuJDuqVUswwl0PcTh33-NyBtYGUp2pe5gMkndxc28RrSlq=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We went with Pearce for our furnace and heat pump replacement, and the experience was excellent from start to finish. Brian was fantastic at explaining the details and offering thoughtful suggestions on the best models for our home. The installation team (Victor and Ben) did an outstanding job, and their professionalism and passion for their work really stood out. It’s no surprise Pearce has such a high rating. Highly recommend them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Larissa Ruiz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL-spXYzLV1nJ3AfDhlgycFJWv38oyxstrmhldQUy9LGjTumA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pearce Heating is an amazing, reliable company to work with. Every single employee is kind and knowledgeable.  Their work is outstanding! Highly recommended. They have installed our heat pump and continue to service our home. They offered the most competitive estimate and we have never been more pleased with a job than with them.  They are very professional! Amazing!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vinay Deo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK3avCWiY-kGPl2xioTcsvRsj3S4QtVXpfKubq1BcjoznZGgw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I got a furnace replaced recently from Pearce Heating and am very pleased with the overall process and experience. They were referred by my neighbors and are small company. Everyone at Pearce Heating I worked with as highly professional and sincere. Clair who prepared the quote was patient as I went through my decision process. What I liked the most was that he explained the rationale behind his recommendation to make sure I was selecting the right model (which was mid=tier, not the top tier).  James and Ben did the install and were amazing. They worked through the day diligently, left the place neat and clean, ensured everything was working right. When I mentioned that in the past the exit end of the condensation drain pipe (outside the home) had frozen, they add some extra insulation to prevent recurrence. A small gesture but shows they don't cut corners and want to make sure the job is done right. Highly recommended.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Old Tinkerer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKok9aXEwNaqE-iW1doQXjEuEVlY6HnEtsEvpmegejZyhWaYQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Pearce team was great from start to finish. They communicated well, educated me on the systems and choices and then followed through on time with excellent quality work. The install team was cheerful and professional and were very careful when inside the house, coming and going into the crawlspace. They identified a defect the builder had made and corrected it. They were very thorough. I would definitely recommend them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jason Allen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIUlm2qU1cSSnmpB_nOKgbsnKsJe_lmuIN4aq_BtG72Xrc9yw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a house generator interlock and gas hookup installed and Brian and his team were excellent! Great communication, fair price, very efficient and thorough, and performed a detailed walkthrough of how to setup and use the generator system once they were done. They made sure the place was in better shape than when they arrived. I highly recommend them and would not take my business anywhere else.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Matthew Guindon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVZkyiZlUJRcMI7rxd9ynFkiSwRsBvxthDN0-oRAlJRCwGdG84=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Outstanding. Pearce installed a new heat pump and gas furnace and did some duct revisions to ensure better health for the whole system. I got 4 quotes in total from highly respected hvac companies and Pearce was an easy choice. Brian is super knowledgeable and was patient with my laundry list of questions before accepting the quote. The install team did a great job. The system is working great. When the county permit person came said, “oh Pearce did this? This will be no problem, they are the best in the business.”","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
