ith the tankless water heater were shown and explained.  All the rusted galvanized steel plumbing that caused a sudden leak was replaced with PEX, system flushed and tested.  Would recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Portia Gray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUyPL6vL4UzXoIavgVX2UnesoNrSw-qlC4rIn2KlSRMO_JTPmE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Herb is a busy guy… and for good reason. He is a knowledgeable plumber who gets to the bottom of things. He doesn’t shy away from a problem and he is fair and reasonable. You will not regret calling Herb for your plumbing needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John Codling","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXQxNsHdPr8_j5yuw_HGbNzkchPbe1vxbsu6oNryLZjr9JHU56V=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great communication to set up the job, showed up as planned and did a great job. Charged a fair rate. Was helpful in discussing the issue and other related things to help me get the most out of the appointment. Would recommend to anyone looking for a quality plumber.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mike Bloom","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWIyz_2sbRAlCTuO6FiskxwqXmmimUrG5I_teKN5eu80fRShzTuUg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"When I need a plumber, Butterfield Plumbing is who I call. When others ask me for a plumbing referral, Butterfield Plumbing is the one. They re-piped my house, have done small repairs and added a gas line. They are reasonably priced and reasonably quick to respond. I happen to know Herb personally and the type of person he is, he's an honest hard working dude that believes in doing it right, not a money grabbing dick. Reviews of his company demonstrates that. Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Corey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL5dk4EuW-R6jHRTVqbb1o1kDTO3toZy00QYAVjN2KcGRV2Ig=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had 4 quotes to run a gas line to my kitchen range and chose Butterfield. All 4 quotes were within 20% of each other. All 4 companies had fantastic reviews. What sold me was that Paul was the only estimator that would be doing the work. It was a no-brainer. I didn't have to worry about an estimate getting confused from the estimator to the contractor performing the work.\nThe job turned out absolutely perfect. Paul even found a gas leak at the meter and called PSE for me. I also called PSE and they came right out and fixed the leak.\n\nI can't think of a single issue with the install. Paul was polite, kiddo friendly, on-time, and honest. And I can now run a gas stove in my kitchen!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jerry McShurley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVFE0irU_j4Y3Vffjv8LaQR_LgEx7Y5woMeHFi9WoSZvIpkaXzY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We asked them to take a look at a small bath room remodel and they went above and beyond.  set the tub AND surround, corrected poorly installed drains.  Did a great job at a great value.  Thank You!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Zack McGlothern","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU2ZvnQYU0_gB7VKulUdm-mPfK-L638QPDoAKk-OvRyj0sVN1nc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Thank you Herb for coming out at 7:00 at night and very timely at that!\n\nVery professional and courteous, and they replaced the broken supply line on our toilet right away.\n\nWe will definitely be using them for all of our  plumbing needs, emergency or not!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
