Rating":5,"Description":"Raymark truly hits the mark - 100%. We recently had our main water line replaced, and the entire experience was outstanding from start to finish. From our first call, their team was professional, responsive, and easy to work with.\nTy, the lead technician, was courteous and highly professional when providing the quote. He took the time to thoroughly explain the details, presented clear options, and never pressured us in any direction.\nErnesto handled the installation and was friendly, efficient, and meticulous. He walked us through the completed work to ensure everything met our expectations and left the area so clean it looked like he had never been there.\nTrustworthy is the best word we can use to describe Raymark. They have absolutely earned our confidence and will be our plumbers from here on out.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joe In Real Life","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKreU0j2X0Vpr60kRG7XvxekfH_NSLTy9EojK9Tz36cLDYrwA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a sudden flood in our basement bathroom and Raymark Plumbing came through big time. Bella at reception was wonderful and got us on the schedule right away, and Tristan and Zander were at our house within about 90 minutes. They found the problem quickly, explained everything clearly, and fixed it fast. The quote was honest and the price was very reasonable. Great service from start to finish—we’ll absolutely call Raymark again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Todd Gates","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUboZEK1iwhoKi1Cykhyv9yHIH58KJ0VlTZZDEAwsVmDSv8ca4p=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My friend Robin doesn't leave reviews but asked me to post this for her, as she feels this team deserves recognition. She met Ronald first, and he was incredibly clear and patient in explaining her sewer issue. Andrew, the Utility Director, provided steady oversight and came in person to look at the site. Both have been timely, responsive, and professional throughout. Their communication has made the process much easier for her to navigate, and she is grateful to have a team this reliable involved in the work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kevin Turco","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWkFxnigUMBIJn4SFCMbjdAfcQTc-apiw_V-hS1z1GCus0o4Q8q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This team is great! Ronald (sewer) and John (plumbing) assessed a water backup that I recently had, and were able to get it all sorted quickly, while explaining the issues and options openly and practically. They went above and beyond to build confidence and trust and, most importantly solve the issues without needing to redo my entire water system. Recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amber Yeaw","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIVR9FhxCS_pCWLG5XkU3ZksK-Yn9UenmPCDPLJJA6cA01sKEZm=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an excellent experience with Raymark.  They were professional and very communicative throughout the whole process.  I had to wait a few weeks for some uncommon parts to arrive and they updated me regularly so I knew I wasn't forgotten.  They did a great job on the installation too.  A few weeks later, I noticed some water on the bathroom floor.  They sent a team out that same day to look at it.  They quickly identified that the leak was from another source but never treated me with any irritation or unkindness.  I'm thoroughly impressed and will always use Raymark!  Their customer service team is amazing too.  :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Josh Vasquez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUoDbaaWap9OCUZdhGqFKfdjSgmlFyIAx-Ys5d3upf-Er9j-ZKq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had Raymark come out for an urgent leak at my home. After getting an outrageous quote from another company I was relieved to have Ryan provide a thorough assessment at a very reasonable price. Nick did an amazing job, the quality exceeded my expectations. 10/10 would work with again!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Anya Buell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI_zkIOwmXK40RD643LmtydAdbNG6XnEOtlLwFHdI7XM0AfLA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I couldn’t be happier with the service I received. From the moment he arrived, he made me feel completely at ease and took the time to really listen and explain things clearly. He worked incredibly hard to track down the problem and didn’t stop until he figured it out—truly going above and beyond what I expected.\n\nOn top of that, he was clean, thorough, and respectful of my space. He was also friendly, personable, and genuinely funny, which made what could have been a stressful situation surprisingly pleasant. It’s rare to find someone who combines skill, work ethic, and great customer service so well. I would absolutely recommend him to anyone needing a plumber.\n\n-Anya","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chris Rose","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbdda_FntX2RIhg9egsyxY41BRQPrzQN5iNGhj6LLekhtWs6QW=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Raymark has treated us very well ad does an excellent job. Today we had Ernesto make several repairs that prevented a major facility flood. Unlike other companies he did not try to upsell me. Raymark will be getting a lot more work at our facilities.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn13JKgUOG20vjEU1iOGHj6d_JoqSS4JF3y_NWUWGorBMhw9a_LqgU-ujbNyFn2G93T9FB2T2p0ikdEQfv13Y90cNt4q7aw98YRsIQhVs3MV1_Tk5YG0w0o6OpH2Y6cVS6vRGfE=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3din700LtYJ9yccPFD5HuS3mxny8HAbziydLjEB2iZGzt-Et-XGyDGs5vkgyGlvnPZzKZRl7D6Hz4hEAN1Z5_EmJb78_zhjO0CDKyHLNMzRAhqRZyen5wVFX5_95R8FIcjG3kT=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0Xk7FO-SU1EmFsIwyELGfvwzVuQ7K6fbwyRFCev7gKeSYwW9SbbfqQv2xFuQ9qyCb8Lci9qNMhHdfxnlUjtQq_jwFomzz51XrRERmO