se person. Would highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kat Berton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIqJHsZrt-FdcPal_cPIl1gJKF4A16jkQZT8rS3D54dZ6iynw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Chuck cleared a drain for us and went above and beyond - cleared another drain he happened to notice was draining slow, gave me lots of great tips on how to best treat other appliances, and was an overall delight to talk to.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Matthew Taylor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJO5ZPlrDw0rueKvQnsVT-iWdE2Xdpq1pnBMRiWTwt7ugH5Ig=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Chuck and the rest of the folks at Green Lake Sewer \u0026 Drain are absolutely fantastic. They are professional, fast, hardworking, honest, and affordable. I have a 75-year-old sewer system, and I wouldn't trust anyone else to handle it after the amazing service they provided me. I can't recommend them enough.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gary Chyan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVgovPnl4ifMTu1oxUCgTqBGAGNbXYkLKVin69-SwKmw4tzt9iEKQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Knowledgable, professional, and quick! As a classic no frills New Yorker, Chuck was super personable and honest with his assessment of the drain problem I had. He was able to quickly diagnose the situation and resolve it without upselling me services I didn't need. Definitely earned my future business!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Derek Bos","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVQ8CVxPI5HPhITh3fblolFy6GlFKvURjk02on0ammqdKSX-VAwaw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Chuck came out next day to help unclog my aunts drain. Friendly and professional. Helpful and reasonable priced. Recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"MaryBeth Tellefson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLGpKJ7xKaPeDQMy8UtMOoGHFY2SKENvGJbRfljY9ormnynnBGG=s120-c-r